column1: Data for Figure S5: Comparison between available regulatory POD values (PODreg,BMDh) and estimated PODp05BMDh (A-B), PODp15BMDh (C-D), PODp25BMDh (E-F), PODp35BMDh (G-H), differentiating between general non-cancer effects (left side, n=744) and reproductive/developmental effects (right side, n=41). The black line represents the 1:1 line, while the red line is the best fit.
